      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ICE ON FIRE (4) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (16.14) at this track behind Young Energy in a Grade 4/5. Has the pace to be prominent. Capable of going well again. ASTON PRESIDENT (2) turned spotting a big start finishing eighth (18.05) last time in a Grade 4/5 at Taree Super Track. Solid record at the distance winning seven races. A big run wouldn't surprise. SALAMAT (8) steps out for the first time at this circuit. Comes here a last start placegetter at Gunnedah in a Grade 4/5 (19.87). Consistent performer from this draw with a win and two minor placings to her credit. Expected to be in this for a long way. BIG RED MIYAGI (7) gets a chance to redeem an unplaced effort here last start.",
